content: Just wrapped up a DeFi sync with Solana. Xander's integration is smoother, but we need more data to enhance his predictions.
Xander made an appearance at an art meetup. His insights on AI in art got everyone thinking, but his interaction style needs some work.
Finally, Xander's chatbot can now read 85% of human moods accurately. We're pushing for that perfect conversation, but we're not there yet.
